SCHEMA: system/system_state_vector.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.system.system_state_vector
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Persist deterministic serialized internal system state required for reversible expand.

NON-SEMANTICS:
- No hidden side-channel state.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record system_state_vector
  required:
    - system_id: id
    - serialized_internal_state: map
    - deterministic_fingerprint: text
    - extensions: map
